  "response": "This is subjective, as different people find different games challenging, but some games often cited as extremely difficult include:\n\n1. Dark Souls series - Known for brutal combat and unforgiving gameplay\n\n2. Ninja Gaiden (NES version) - Extremely challenging action game with precise mechanics\n\n3. Super Meat Boy - Precision platformer with very tight controls and difficult levels\n\n4. Battletoads - Notorious for its extreme difficulty, especially certain levels\n\n5. I Wanna Be The Guy - A fan-made game designed to be nearly impossible\n\n6. Cuphead - Challenging run-and-gun game with difficult boss battles\n\n7. Ghosts 'n Goblins - Classic arcade game known for its punishing difficulty\n\n8. Sekiro: Shadows Die Twice - Another FromSoftware game with extreme challenge\n\n9. Contra (original) - Infamous for its near-impossible difficulty without cheats\n\n10. Maldita Castilla - Extremely tough retro-style platformer\n\nThe \"hardest\" game can depend on individual skill, game design, and personal experience. What's extremely difficult for one player might be manageable for another.",
